# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Private/Custom Packages (GitHub Packages)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED: GitHub Personal Access Token for @rev9dev-netizen packages
# 
# To get your token:
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens
# 2. Click "Generate new token" → "Generate new token (classic)"
# 3. Name it: "CloudClash Dev Access"
# 4. Select scopes: ✅ read:packages (and write:packages if publishing)
# 5. Click "Generate token"
# 6. Copy the token (ghp_xxxx...) and paste below
# 
# ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Never commit this token to git!
# The .env file is gitignored to protect your token.
#
NPM_TOKEN="your_github_token_here"
